    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Species of medium-size to large deciduous, coniferous larch tree native to western Russia, reaching 20-50 m tall. Hardy in cold weather and rot resistant.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
